speech: Here is a short description about Rheneas. Rheneas is a fictional locomotive from The Railway Series by Rev. W. Awdry and the children's TV series Thomas & Friends. He is one of the oldest engines on the Island of Sodor. Rheneas lives and works on the Skarloey Railway as Engine No.2, and is known as the "Gallant Old Engine" because he saved the railway from closure. He is Skarloey's brother.
